<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Perturbation" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Perturbation,</orth> disturbance, disorder, disquiet: <cit><quote>horror and p. follows her,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 2.1.268" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado II, 1, 268</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>p. of the brain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.132" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 132</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>O polished p., golden care,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 4.5.23" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 5, 23</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>fills thy sleep with --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.161" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 161</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a great p. in nature,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 10</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>